  "title": "Sales and Marketing Engineer #78075",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturing/ Production</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Sales and Marketing Engineer</strong></li><li>Working Location: North - Seletar (Nearest MRT: Khatib)</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days / Monday to Friday, 8.30 am – 5.45 pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to SGD 7000 + Performance Bonus (Min. 1 month)</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Promote the company’s engineering and MRO capabilities to aircraft manufacturers, operators, and MROs across the Asia-Pacific region</li><li>Recommend optimal, comprehensive avionics system solutions for customers’ existing or new aircraft, collaborating with the company’s skilled engineering team</li><li>Work closely with the engineering team to understand customer requirements and develop tailored avionics system solutions</li><li>Prepare and present technical proposals, quotations, and product demonstrations to potential clients</li><li>Manage client relationships and ensure high levels of customer satisfaction</li><li>Monitor industry trends and competitors to identify new business opportunities</li><li>Support project planning and ensure smooth communication between the sales and engineering departments</li><li></li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Min. Diploma in Avionics, Aerospace Engineering, Electrical Engineering, or a related field</li><li>Min. 2 years of working experience in related field</li><li>Prior experience in avionics systems design, engineering, or a similar technical background</li><li>Demonstrated marketing and/or sales experience within the aviation or aerospace industry</li><li>Strong understanding of FAA, EASA, or military design standards and regulatory environments</li><li>Experience in managing engineering design projects and coordinating with technical teams is a plus</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#78075 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
